annotationA: Hsc70Cb, isoform G; Hsc70Cb is an HSP110 family protein, and interacts physically with DnaJ-1 as a chaperone of misfolded proteins. Hsc70Cb functions together with DnaJ-1 to prevent the toxicity of aggregation-prone proteins
annotationB: Mrj, isoform E; Unfolded protein binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: protein folding
